narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 111 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 111 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: This is a great overview of corporate financial strategy and provides a base of understanding for those that are interested in finance.

DEFINITELY take this class if you get in. You will learn so much, be challenged by SOM peers, and there is no final. You will work hard during the year but it's so worth it. I've used this information in quite a few job interviews already. If you are considering finance or consulting - must take.
